snippet.title: Version 1.3 Trailer - "Celestial Eyes Above Mortal Ruins" | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
The jade mirror hangs high in the sky, reflecting the remnants of calamity in the world. Even as the stars shift and turn, the shadows of the past disasters have not dissipated.

English Voice:
Yukong — Dawn M. Bennett
Fu Xuan — Sarah Wiedenheft
Dan Heng • Imbibitor Lunae — Nicholas Leung
Herta — PJ Mattson
